column2: "Oh, welcome back. Did you get the ingredients? I'm so glad."
"Wow! This rice is so shiny and clean, and the grains are so big! And these tomatoes smell wonderful!"
"Yes, these will be perfect! Franka said she'd give me the other ingredients and some seasonings."
"Hehe, I think this is going to be delicious. You were very helpful. Thank you so much!"
